uk.ac.kent.models.records

Class EmploymentDetailsRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.kent.models.records.BaseRecord
      • uk.ac.kent.models.records.EmploymentDetailsRecord

  • @Entity
public final class EmploymentDetailsRecord
extends BaseRecord
    Each Employee has a single EmploymentDetailsRecord associated with her. It stores all information about the current employment details.
    Author:
    norbert
